				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I remember so many time dying because our healer healed the mob instead of the tank.  This doesn't happen anymore.
<br />

<br />
So.  I'm prepping my first effort at the end-game of Prayer Shawl #8.
<br />

<br />
I've read several things and I still don't know this answer, so a touch of help is appreciated.
<br />

<br />
Can we drop a Virtue on the General and then heal him as needed?  It just strikes me that this encounter is much easier if he is heal-able.
<br />

<br />
 <img src="images/smiles/icon_question.gif" alt="Question" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
